  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  occurrence of injury between 2005 and 2011

          -  burn surface area (BSA) greater than 10%

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy, renal or liver failure, hypo or hyperparathyroidism, prior vitamin D
             substitution, treatment using systemic corticosteroids or antiepileptic drugs, regular
             exposure to ultraviolet B radiation (solarium), unstable cardiovascular disease or
             acute muscle or skeletal injury prohibiting physical exercise
      </textblock>
